# Install Google Chrome

* Download google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb from [https://www.google.com/chrome/browser/desktop/index.html](https://www.google.com/chrome/browser/desktop/index.html)
* Goto the Downloads directory cd ~/Downloads
* sudo dpkg -i google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
* If there are missing prerequisites: sudo apt-get -f install
* Remove downloaded package: rm google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb 
